movie.title: America's Sweethearts
movie.tagLine: Hollywood's hottest couple just split up. It'll take more than special effects to reunite them.
movie.summary: In the midst of a nasty public breakup of married movie stars, a studio publicist scrambles to put a cap on the escalating situation as the couple's latest film has found it's only print kidnapped by the director.
